  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 375°f (190°c).",
    "arrange the unsalted butter, softened, on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "place the baking sheet in the oven and bake for 10 minutes, or until the butter is golden brown and fragrant.",
    "remove the baking sheet from the oven and let it cool slightly.",
    "in a large bowl, whisk together the honey, Ukrainian-style, the grated carrot, the dried cranberries, the sour cream, the eggs, the vanilla extract, the plain flour, the baking powder, the ground cinnamon, the ground ginger, the kosher salt, the freshly squeezed orange juice, the freshly squeezed lemon juice, and the water.",
    "add the melted unsalted butter to the bowl and whisk until well combined.",
    "add the ground cardamom, the ground cloves, the ground nutmeg, the black pepper, the raspberry jam, the honey, additional, the orange marmalade, the lemon curd, the whipped cream, the chocolate chips, the confectioner's sugar, the dried rose petals, the orange flower water, the lemon extract, the orange extract, the ginger extract, the cinnamon stick, the ground ginger, the ground cinnamon, the ground nutmeg, the ground cardamom, the ground cloves, the black pepper, the salt, the sugar, the flour, the baking powder, the baking soda, the kosher salt, the unsalted butter, melted, and the honey, additional to the bowl and whisk until well combined.",
    "transfer the mixture to a tagine pot and smooth the top.",
    "place the tagine pot in the oven and bake for 20 minutes, or until the mixture is set and the edges are golden brown.",
    "remove the tagine pot from the oven and let it cool slightly.",
    "serve the citrusy fruity gooey ukrainian butter tagine warm, garnished with the dried cranberry-orange relish, the homemade orange-cranberry jam, the store-bought orange marmalade, the homemade lemon curd, the whipped cream, the chocolate chips, the confectioner's sugar, the dried rose petals, the orange flower water, the lemon extract, the orange extract, the ginger extract, the cinnamon stick, the ground ginger, the ground cinnamon, the ground nutmeg, the ground cardamom, the ground cloves, the black pepper, the salt, the sugar, the flour, the baking powder, the baking soda, the kosher salt, the unsalted butter, melted, and the honey, additional.",
    "note: this recipe makes 12 servings."
  ],
